      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Learn the Lance",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Alright, Ace, lesson time!\r\nA knight wields their lance to\r\nprotect the weak\u2014just like a\r\n\u003CCOL RED\u003ERathian\u003C/COL\u003E fiercely protects her\r\nyoung! Capture the queen\r\nand you\u0027ll acquire some new\r\nSkills for your lance!",
        "Target": "Capture a Rathian",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, time expires,\r\nor capture target slain"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le\u00E7on Lance",
        "Client": "Utsushi le ma\u00EEtre",
        "Description": "Bon, je t\u0027explique ! Un chevalier\r\ndoit se servir de sa lance pour\r\nprot\u00E9ger les faibles, comme\r\nune \u003CCOL RED\u003ERathian\u003C/COL\u003E prot\u00E8ge ses petits !\r\nCapture la reine et tu pourras\r\napprendre de nouveaux Talents\r\npour ta lance !",
        "Target": "Capturer une Rathian",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9\r\nCible tu\u00E9e"
